🌸 reminders in lyrics 🌸

  • “I’ll be strong, I’ll be wrong, oh but life goes on”

  • “No one notices until it’s too late to do anything”
  • “You walk around here thinking you’re not pretty, but that’s not true”
  • “You’re beautiful, every little piece love, dont you know, you’re really gonna be someone”
  • “Capture it, remember it”

  • “Don’t forget to look before you fall”
  • “I’ve found time can heal most anything”
  • “Take a deep breath girl”
  • “This ain’t a fairytale”
  • “I’m gonna find someone someday who might actually treat me well”
  • “You’ve got a smile that could light up this whole town”
  • “People are people and sometimes we change our minds”
  • “It’s never simple, never easy”
  • “People are people and sometimes it doesn’t work out”
  • “I believe in whatever you do”
  • “Things will change”
  • “The time will come for us to finally win”
  • “Fight for what we’ve worked for all these years”
  • We’ll stand up champions tonight”
  • “I’ll never leave you alone”
  • “I’d go back in time and change it but I can’t”
  • “I’m shining like fireworks over your sad empty town”
  • “Someday I’ll be living in a big ole city”
  • “Miscommunications lead to fallout”
  • “Don’t you ever grow up”
  • “Don’t make her drop you off around the block, remember that she’s getting older too”
  • “Take pictures in your mind of your childhood room, memorise what it sounded like when your dad gets home, remember the footsteps, remember the words said, and all your little brother’s favourite songs”
  • “I just realised everything I have is someday gonna be gone”
  • “Sophistication isn’t what you wear or who you know”
  • “It’s alright, just wait and see”
  • “Your string of lights are still bright to me”
  • “Who you are is not where you’ve been”

  • “Everything will be alright”
  • “Good girls, hopeful they’ll be, and king they will wait”

  • “What’s past is past”
  • “You can want who you want, boys and boys and girls and girls”

  • “Could end in burning flames or paradise”
  • “We were built to fall apart then fall back together”

  • “When you’re young you just run but you come back to what you need”
  • “Love’s a fragile little flame, it could burn out”
  • “Let them say what they want, we can’t hear it”
  • “Loose lips sink ships all the damn time”
  • “We’re bulletproof”
  • “Just because you’re clean don’t mean you don’t miss it”
  • “I bury hatchets but I keep maps of where I put ‘em”
  • “Never trust a narcissist”
  • “IF A MAN TALKS SHIT THEN I OWE HIM NOTHING”

  • “You’re gorgeous”

summary: Okay so I’ve been thinking about this a while, and I’m not sure if anyone else does this or if I’m just crazy but I felt like...
body:
Okay so I’ve been thinking about this a while, and I’m not sure if anyone else does this or if I’m just crazy but I felt like sharing.

So I’ve got favorite eras; but then within that I’ve got favorite points in each era, Xavier hair, favorite style, etc. And I was just sat here and I thought “what would but accumulation of favorites piled into one be?” So here it is.

Favorite: Red era hair, 1989 street style, Speak Now interviews, Fearless Documentary, Rep music (+Red bonus tracks), Red costumes, Rep tour, Rep vibe, Rep events/award ceremonies.

So yeah I’m probably the only person who does this, but if I could compile an ideal era it would literally be this.


I know some of these things hella wouldn’t go together like Rep tour with Red costumes but just let me be imaginative okayy.

So yeah I’m probably the only person who does this, but if I could compile an ideal era it would literally be this.


I know some of these things hella wouldn’t go together like Rep tour with Red costumes but just let me be imaginative okayy.
